data.description: Welcome Home!!  This two-story home provides very high ceiling, 4 large bedrooms with walk in closets, plus a large loft and 2.5 baths. The main level living area offers hard wood floors in the entry and into the kitchen area. The main level also offers an office. The kitchen boasts beautiful cabinetry, a large pantry and a built-in island with ample seating space. Upstairs, you'll find the owners suite which features a deluxe bath and large walk-in closet.  3 car garage and full basement provide all of the extra storage you need! Oversized fenced back yard, large patio with a gazebo!   Hurry this home won't last long!
